&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note: This role is 100% in-office, primarily out of our Wakefield, RI (235 Main Street) and Charlestown, RI (4009 Old Post Road) offices.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
